2}{\cf1\afs28\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs28\loch\f5
 It is a discipline that lies at the interface of computational complexity and various areas of discrete mathematics such as model theory, logic, universal algebra, or ramsey theory. The interaction between the two sides has been fruitful in both directions. On the one hand, it is notoriously hard to obtain general results in complexity theory but the connection of CSPs with discrete mathematics has led to elegant solutions to complexity-theoretic questions that were open for decades. On the other hand, the study of CSPs has motivated questions and influenced the research in discrete mathematics, most notably in universal algebra and Ramsey theory.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f3\fs24\lang2057\qj\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\cf1\afs28\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs28\loch\f5

