Barto, Opr\u353\'9aal and Pinsker proved that for omega-categorical structures, uniformly continuous homomorphisms encode complexity reductions, and in particular homomorphisms to the clone of projections encode NP-hardness proofs. This is what I will call \u8220\'93algebraic hardness\u8221\'94.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1081\loch\f3\fs24\lang2057\qj\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\cf1\afs28\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs28\loch\f5

